snippet.textDisplay: PLEASE READ! For the 3 point shot, i feel they could have done a way more fun game for the prize money . Its called 500. The rules to the game are as follows: Everyone lines up on the 3 point line, and starting clockwise shoots the 3 pointer. If the person makes the basket, the next person has a bounty of 100 points to them however if that person also makes the shot, that bounty gets sent to the next person. If that person misses, they are stuck with those 200 points. If a person airballs a 3 pointer, they give themselves 100 points (or 200 if there are lot of people playing to make the game go by faster.) Any player that gets 500 points to them are eliminated until one is left standing.
